Package: aiImageDetect
Title: AI versus Human Image Detector
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Alan", "Inglis", email = "alan.n.inglis@gmail.", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a wrapper around a vision transformer fine-tuned to
    distinguish AI-generated from photographic images.  The package bridges R to
    PyTorch through reticulate and installs the required Python stack on first use.
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.36)
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
